				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Depends on what I'm making. Usually I can just rely on Schism Tracker, but this doesn't work as well when pitch modulation and/or noise generation is involved (thankfully I assigned these to unused IDs, to the original Impulse Tracker's standards...). Sometimes I have to convert them while they're incomplete to make sure my pitch modulation (and/or noise generation) is working correctly. Other times I convert them only when they're finished and ready to go.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
